            "heading": "13. PRIVACY POLICY AND COMMUNICATIONS",
            "content": "<p>Please see our <a href=\"/pages/privacy-statement\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Privacy Statement\">privacy policy</a>.<br/>When you provide us with your email address or mobile phone number, you may opt in to electronic communications in respect of news, promotions, wishlist reminders, bag reminders and updates on the status of returns and refunds.  We may also communicate with you electronically in as set out in the Privacy Policy.  Your consent to receipt of certain communications may be implied from the use of certain functional aspects of our service.</p>",
